OL,3,CMan found guilty of manslaughter after
OL,4,CEllesmere Port stabbing
OL,6,FA man has been found guilty of
OL,7,Fmanslaughter after stabbing another
OL,8,Fman to death in Ellesmere Port.
OL,10,FBen Ruddock, 20, from Great Sutton was
OL,11,Ffound not guilty of murdering Lloyd
OL,12,FVelasquez, but guilty of manslaughter
OL,13,Fat a trial at Chester Crown Court.
OL,15,FMr Velasquez, who was 34 and was just
OL,16,Fabout to become a father, was attacked
OL,17,Fin May last year. He died later in
OL,18,Fhospital.
