OL,3,CMan found guilty of manslaughter after
OL,4,CEllesmere Port stabbing
OL,6,FReacting to Ruddock's conviction,
OL,7,FLloyd's mother said: "There are no
OL,8,Fwords to describe the amount of hurt
OL,9,Fand heartache Lloyd's death has left,
OL,10,Fnot only for his immediate family,
OL,11,Frelatives and close friends, but for
OL,12,Fhis baby son, born just nine weeks
OL,13,Fafter Lloyd was tragically killed on
OL,14,Fthat fateful day on 1 May 2024.
OL,26,@oD@VOU
