OL,4,CEllesmere Port stabbing
OL,6,FLater, Lloyd and his friend were
OL,7,Fdriving along Hollybush Way, Ellesmere
OL,8,FPort, when they saw Ruddock, who was
OL,9,Fwith two other men. A confrontation
OL,10,Foccurred, and Ruddock produced a knife
OL,11,Ffrom his waistband and brandished it
OL,12,Ftowards Lloyd, who got back into the
OL,13,Fcar and left.
