OL,3,CMan found guilty of manslaughter after
OL,4,CEllesmere Port stabbing
OL,6,FLloyd's friend received further voice
OL,7,Fnotes in which Ruddock made more
OL,8,Fthreats to harm Lloyd. Minutes later,
OL,9,FLloyd and his female friend were
OL,10,Fdriving along Summertrees Road when
OL,11,Fthey again saw Ruddock and the two
OL,12,Fmen. Another altercation ensued.
OL,13,FDuring the incident, Ruddock produced
OL,14,Fthe knife and stabbed Lloyd. He then
OL,15,Fran from the scene.
OL,17,FParamedics and officers attended and
OL,18,FLloyd was taken to hospital where he
OL,19,Fwas sadly pronounced dead.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
