OL,3,CMan found guilty of manslaughter after
OL,4,CEllesmere Port stabbing
OL,6,FA post-mortem later revealed Lloyd
OL,7,Fdied from a stab wound to the chest.
OL,8,FRuddock was charged with murder the
OL,9,Fsame day. The two men who were with
OL,10,FRuddock on the evening of the incident
OL,11,Fwere arrested at the time but later
OL,12,Freleased with no further action
OL,13,Fagainst them.
OL,15,FRuddock was instead found guilty of
OL,16,Fmanslaughter and will be sentenced at
OL,17,FChester Crown Court on Monday 24 March.
OL,19,FFollowing the guilty verdict for
OL,20,Fmanslaughter, Detective Inspector
OL,21,FAndrea Price said:
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
