OL,3,CMan found guilty of manslaughter after
OL,4,CEllesmere Port stabbing
OL,6,F"The incident itself was over in a
OL,7,Fmatter of seconds ` and this should
OL,8,Fserve as a warning of the dangers of
OL,9,Fknife crime.
OL,11,F"Instead of owning up to what he had
OL,12,Fdone, he chose to flee Cheshire.
OL,13,FThankfully he was later arrested in
OL,14,FMerseyside and now, as a result of our
OL,15,Finvestigation and the evidence against
OL,16,Fhim, he has been found guilty of the
OL,17,Fmanslaughter of Lloyd.
OL,19,F"Our thoughts remain with Lloyd's
OL,20,Ffamily and friends at this time."
